org.mozilla.mentat

Class TupleResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mozilla.mentat.TupleResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CollResult

    public class TupleResult
extends Object
    Wraps a `Tuple` result from a Mentat query. A `Tuple` result is a single row TypedValues. Values for individual fields can be fetched as TypedValue or converted into a requested type.

    Field values can be fetched as one of the following types:

    • TypedValue
    • long
    • Entid (as long)
    • Keyword (as String)
    • boolean
    • double
    • Date
    • String
    • UUID

    To iterate over the result set use standard iteration flows.
